<plot>Two shy romantics meet online, but can't seem to connect in real life. They send each other flirtatious texts and emails while they unwittingly trace each other's steps throughout New York City, but it takes a dream to finally bring them face-to-face. The story is told through music, dance and text messages.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?423236</url></doc>
